title: Softy from Seattle loves Jake Browning!
description: Dave "Softy" Mahler is an elite radio host on KJR in Seattle, our sister station. He's also a Washington Huskies encyclopedia and has a huge opinion on Vikings UDFA QB Jake Browning! He shares it with PA #92Noon!
